OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will stay
OL,6,Fcloudy through the evening and also
OL,7,Fovernight with further outbreaks of
OL,8,Frain, which will be heavy at times.
OL,9,FWindy at times, especially towards
OL,10,Fmorning.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FSome bright spells possible
OL,13,Fat first. Otherwise cloudy and windy
OL,14,Fwith rain, heavy and persistent at
OL,15,Ftimes. Clear spells and blustery
OL,16,Fshowers in the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
