OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FColder
OL,6,Fon Friday and Saturday with bright
OL,7,Fspells and a few showers, these mainly
OL,8,Fin the west. Further rain expected
OL,9,Flater Saturday. Cloudy and windier on
OL,10,FSunday with further rain.
